{"title_page": "Wainunu River", "text_new": "#redirect[[List of rivers of Fiji]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox river\n| name              = Wainunu River\n| image             = \n| image_size        = \n| image_alt         =\n| image_caption     = \n| map               = \n| map_size          = \n| map_alt           =\n| map_caption       = \n| source1_location  = [[Vanua Levu]]\n| mouth_location    = \n| subdivision_type1 = Country\n| subdivision_name1 = [[Fiji]]\n| progression       = \n| length            = \n| source1_elevation = \n| mouth_elevation   = \n| discharge1_avg    = \n| basin_size        = \n| river_system      =\n| tributaries_left  =\n| tributaries_right =\n}}\n'''Wainunu River''' is a river of [[Vanua Levu]], [[Fiji]].\n\n==See also==\n*[[List of rivers of Fiji]]\n\n==References==\n*[http://earth-info.nga.mil/gns/html/index.html GEOnet Names Server]\n\n{{coord|16|51|S|178|55|E|display=title|region:FJ_type:river_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n[[Category:Rivers of Vanua Levu]]\n\n\n{{Fiji-river-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Reywas92", "label": "safe", "comment": "no significant sources for minor feature to passWP:GEOLAND4;WP:NOPAGE", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wainunu_River&redirect=no"}
{"title_page": "Irakli To\u00e7i", "text_new": "{{short description|Albanian footballer}}\n{{Orphan|date=April 2016}}\n\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Irakli To\u00e7i\n| image = \n| fullname = Irakli To\u00e7i\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1981|6|30}}\n| birth_place = [[Elbasan]], [[Albania]]\n| height = \n| position = [[Goalkeeper (football)|Goalkeeper]]\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 = \n| youthclubs1 = \n| years1 = 2002\u20132003\n| years2 = 2003\u20132005\n| years3 = 2005\u20132007\n| years4 = 2007\u20132008\n| years5 = 2008\u20132009\n| years6 = 2009\n| years7 = 2010\n| years8 = 2011\u20132015\n| clubs1 = [[Sopoti Librazhd|Sopoti]]\n| clubs2 = [[KF Elbasani|Elbasani]]\n| clubs3 = [[Luft\u00ebtari Gjirokast\u00ebr FC|Luft\u00ebtari]]\n| clubs4 = Elbasani\n| clubs5 = [[KS Turbina C\u00ebrrik|Turbina]]\n| clubs6 = [[KS Gramozi Ersek\u00eb|Gramozi]]\n| clubs7 = Luft\u00ebtari \n| clubs8 = Elbasani\n| caps1 = \n| caps2 = 18\n| caps3 = 27\n| caps4 = 12\n| caps5 = \n| caps6 = 12\n| caps8 = 9\n| goals1 = \n| goals2 = 0\n| goals3 = 0\n| goals4 = 0\n| goals5 = \n| goals6 = 0\n| goals8 = 0\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 = \n| nationalcaps1 = \n| nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = 14 May 2010\n| ntupdate = \n}}\n\n'''Irakli To\u00e7i''' (born 30 June 1981) is an [[Albania]]n retired [[association football|football]] player who played for [[KS Gramozi Ersek\u00eb]], [[KS Luft\u00ebtari Gjirokast\u00ebr]] and [[KF Elbasani]] in the Albanian Superliga.\n\n==External links==\n*{{FootballDatabase.eu|50384}}\n* [https://fshf.org/garat/?query=info&player_id=214503 Profile] - FSHF\n\n{{use dmy dates|date=December 2010}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Toci, Irakli}}\n[[Category:1981 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Elbasan]]\n[[Category:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football goalkeepers]]\n[[Category:KS Sopoti Librazhd players]]\n[[Category:KF Elbasani players]]\n[[Category:Luft\u00ebtari Gjirokast\u