y:Albanian footballers]]\n[[Category:KF La\u00e7i players]]\n[[Category:KF Erzeni players]]\n[[Category:Albanian Superliga players]]\n[[Category:Albanian First Division players]]\n\n\n{{Albania-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name        = Elton Vata\n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|1998|4|13|df=y}}\n| birth_place = [[Kuk\u00ebs]], [[Albania]]\n| position    = [[Goalkeeper (association football)|Goalkeeper]]\n| currentclub = [[KF Erzeni|Erzeni]]\n| clubnumber  = 12\n| youthyears1 = 2011-2014 | youthclubs1 = [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta]]\n| years1 = 2014\u20132016\n| clubs1 = [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta]]\n| caps1 = 0\n| goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2016\u20132018\n| clubs2 = [[KF La\u00e7i|La\u00e7i]]\n| caps2 = 8\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2018\u2013\n| clubs3 = [[KF Erzeni|Erzeni]]\n| caps3 = 33\n| goals3 = 0\n| pcupdate       = {{date|2019-11-21}}\n}}\n'''Elton Vata''' (born 13 April 1998) is an [[Albania]]n [[Association football|footballer]] who plays for [[KF Erzeni|Erzeni Shijak]] as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.joueurs.elton.vata.254104.en.html|title=Elton Vata|publisher=}}</ref>\n\n==Club career==\n===KF La\u00e7i===\nIn September 2016, Vata joined [[Albanian Superliga]] club [[KF La\u00e7i]]. He made his league debut for the club on 26 November 2016 in a 1-0 away loss to [[KF Sk\u00ebnderbeu Kor\u00e7\u00eb|Sk\u00ebnderbeu Kor\u00e7\u00eb]]. He played all ninety minutes of the match.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2016/11/26/albania/super-league/kf-laci/ks-skenderbeu-korce/2342627/|title=Laci vs. Skenderbeu Korce \u2013 26 November 2016 \u2013 Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com|accessdate=24 July 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|id=elton-vata/395466|name=Elton Vata}}\n* [https://fshf.org/garat/?query=info&player_id=234792 Profile] - FSHF\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vata, Elton}}\n[[Ca